Class ATPMakeCall

java.lang.Object
  od.oracle.apps.xxom.atp.ATPMakeCall

java.lang.Runnable
public class ATPMakeCall
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable

Implements the execution of database PL/SQL procedure. The call is constructed / executed dynamically. The variable - parameter mapping and the PL/SQL procedure metadata is stored.
